== 其它发行版本 ==
碎南瓜的多张正式发行唱片中都收录了《今天》，例如乐队最畅销的唱片《烂苹果》和《连体单曲》（{{lang|en|''Siamese Singles''}}）{{lang|en|[[Boxset|套装]]}}。乐队在故乡[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]现场演出《今天》的录像收录在1994年发行的音乐视频专辑《{{lang|en|Vieuphoria}}》，以及一起发行的唱片《{{lang|en|Earphoria}}》中<ref>{{cite newspaper | title = Entertainment Briefs | work = ''[[芝加哥太阳报|Chicago Sun-Times]]'' | date = 2006-04-17}}</ref>，{{lang|en|Pitchfork}}网站的克里斯·达伦（{{lang|en|Chris Dahlen}}）称赞这是段“凯旋的录音”<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-10-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141016045020/http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/7263-earphoria/ | deadurl = no | url = http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/7263-earphoria/ | title = Smashing Pumpkins: Earphoria | author = Chris Dahlen | publisher = Pitchfork Media | date = 2002-12-12 | accessdate = 2015-03-06 }}</ref>。芝加哥的这次现场演出还有另一个录制版本，收录在宣传专辑《芝加哥现场23.10.95》（{{lang|en|''Live in Chicago''}}）中，并且有14卷《[[碎南瓜乐队|碎南瓜现场]]》专辑中收录了这首歌曲。另外，许多碎南瓜乐队的[[盗版|盗版]]唱片中收录了不同版本的《今天》，例如《拔插：100%纯声学表演》（{{lang|en|''Unplugged: 100% Pure Acoustic Performances''}}）就收录了歌曲的[[原音乐|声学]]录音和非正式的现场录音版本。<ref>{{cite web | author = Prato, Greg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130822235651/http://www.allmusic.com/album/unplugged-100-pure-acoustic-performances-mw0001007134 | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/unplugged-100-pure-acoustic-performances-mw0001007134 | title = Unplugged: 100% Pure Acoustic Performances | publisher = Allmusic | accessdate = 2015-03-06 | archivedate = 2013-08-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

少数合辑唱片中也收录了《今天》。例如由《{{lang|en|Melody Maker}}》（意为《旋律制作商》）赞助汇编的“英国独立音乐[[时间囊|时间囊]]”——“独立歌曲20强”第18卷第4首歌曲就是《今天》<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2015-03-06 | url = http://allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&sql=10:dcfexqqhldse | title = Indie Top 20, Vol. 18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150306035103/http://www.allmusic.com/album/indie-top-20-vol-18-mw0000984487 | author = Kellman, Andy | publisher = Allmusic | accessdate = 2015-03-06 }}</ref>。由[[音乐电视网|音乐电视网]]出品，收录20世纪90年代早期畅销单曲的荷兰进口双碟专辑《{{lang|en|Rock Am Ring}}》也收录了这首歌曲<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130703225952/http://www.allmusic.com/album/rock-am-ring-mw0000907911 | archivedate = 2013-07-03 | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/rock-am-ring-mw0000907911 | title = Rock Am Ring | author = Huey, Steve | publisher = Allmusic | accessdate = 2015-03-06 }}</ref>。

=== 翻唱版本 ===
多张[[纪念专辑|纪念专辑]]中收录了《今天》的[[翻唱|翻唱]]版本。2001年发行的《哥特——工业向碎南瓜乐队致敬》（{{lang|en|''A Gothic–Industrial Tribute to The Smashing Pumpkins''}}）中就收录了[[工业音乐|工业]]乐队闪灵（{{lang|en|Shining}}）诠释的《今天》[[舞曲|舞曲]]版本<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-06-09 | deadurl = no | title = A Gothic Industrial Tribute to the Smashing Pumpkins | author = Huey, Steve | publisher = Allmusic | accessdate = 2015-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120609060353/http://www.allmusic.com/album/a-gothic-industrial-tribute-to-the-smashing-pumpkins-mw0000624940 | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/a-gothic-industrial-tribute-to-the-smashing-pumpkins-mw0000624940 }}</ref>。[[灵魂乐|灵魂]]音乐家[[所罗门·伯克|所罗门·伯克]]（{{lang|en|Solomon Burke}}）的儿子小所罗门·伯克（{{lang|en|Solomon Burke Jr.}}）以[[摩城唱片|摩城]]风格表演了“截然不同”的《今天》版本，该版本收录在专辑《帕奇午夜：向碎南瓜乐队致敬》（{{lang|en|''Midnight in the Patch: Tribute to The Smashing Pumpkins''}}）中<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-12-30 | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/midnight-in-the-patch-tribute-to-smashing-pumpkins-mw0000010976 | title = Midnight in the Patch: Tribute to Smashing Pumpkins | author = Loftus, Johnny | publisher = Allmusic | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121230193820/http://www.allmusic.com/album/midnight-in-the-patch-tribute-to-smashing-pumpkins-mw0000010976 }}</ref>。其他纪念专辑中的《今天》翻唱版本还包括：《你心中的杀手：致敬碎南瓜乐队》（{{lang|en|''The Killer in You: A Tribute to Smashing Pumpkins''}}）中[[睡眠装甲|睡眠装甲]]乐队表演的版本，《幽灵儿童/朋友和敌人》（{{lang|en|''Ghost Children/Friends and Enemies''}}）中{{lang|en|Death Rawk Boy}}表演的版本<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/smashing-pumpkins-tribute-the-killer-in-you-mw0000347576 | title = Smashing Pumpkins Tribute: The Killer in You | author = Prato, Greg | publisher = Allmusic | accessdate = 2015-03-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130604123435/http://www.allmusic.com/album/smashing-pumpkins-tribute-the-killer-in-you-mw0000347576 | archivedate = 2013-06-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.act4.net/ghostchildren2.htm | title = Ghost Children 2: Friends And Enemies - A Tribute to SP | publisher = Act4.net | accessdate = 2015-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150201160000/http://act4.net/ghostchildren2.htm | archivedate = 2015-02-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，日本[[嘻哈音乐|嘻哈]]乐团{{lang|en|[[Dragon_Ash|Dragon Ash]]}}在歌曲《{{lang|en|Grateful Days}}》（意为《感恩岁月》）中采用了《今天》的吉他主题段落<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.spfc.org/songs-releases/discog.html?discog_id=140 | title = Dragon Ash: Grateful Days | publisher = SPFC.org | accessdate = 2015-03-06 | archivedate = 2014-12-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141225010441/http://www.spfc.org/songs-releases/discog.html?discog_id=140 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。[[约翰·克雷吉|约翰·克雷吉]]（{{lang|en|John Craigie}}）的唱片《{{lang|en|Leave the Fire Behind}}》（意为《离开火线》）中也翻唱了《今天》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.homelesstunes.com/john-craigie-leave-the-fire-behind |title=Homeless Tunes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203021427/http://www.homelesstunes.com/john-craigie-leave-the-fire-behind |publisher=homelesstunes.com |archivedate=2013-12-03 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-03-06 }}</ref>。

